# open the Shortcuts app on your Iphone 
# create a new shortcut
# add action
web > Get Contents of URL: 
  URL:https//your-backend-server/chat
  method:POST 
  request Body: JSON with message as the key and your input text as the value. 
# add action
   Scripting > Get Dictionary Value to extract  the response test from the JSON returned by your server
# add action 
  Scripting > show Results to display the response.

**********NOTE********** 

Make sure to replace "YOUR_OPENAI_API_KEY' with your actual OpenAI API key and Deploy the server to a LIVE URL.

